27namespace webrtc {
28class PacketRouter;
29class ProcessThread;
30class RtcEventLog;
31class RtpPacketReceived;
32class RtpStreamReceiverControllerInterface;
33class RtpStreamReceiverInterface;
34
35namespace voe {
36class ChannelReceiveInterface;
37} // namespace voe
38
39namespace internal {
40class AudioSendStream;
41
42class AudioReceiveStream final : public webrtc::AudioReceiveStream,
43 public AudioMixer::Source,
44 public Syncable {
45 public:
46 AudioReceiveStream(Clock* clock,
47 RtpStreamReceiverControllerInterface* receiver_controller,
48 PacketRouter* packet_router,
49 ProcessThread* module_process_thread,
50 NetEqFactory* neteq_factory,
51 const webrtc::AudioReceiveStream::Config& config,
52 const rtc::scoped_refptr<webrtc::AudioState>& audio_state,
53 webrtc::RtcEventLog* event_log);
54 // For unit tests, which need to supply a mock channel receive.
55 AudioReceiveStream(
56 Clock* clock,
57 RtpStreamReceiverControllerInterface* receiver_controller,
58 PacketRouter* packet_router,
59 const webrtc::AudioReceiveStream::Config& config,
60 const rtc::scoped_refptr<webrtc::AudioState>& audio_state,
61 webrtc::RtcEventLog* event_log,
62 std::unique_ptr<voe::ChannelReceiveInterface> channel_receive);
63
64 AudioReceiveStream() = delete;
65 AudioReceiveStream(const AudioReceiveStream&) = delete;
66 AudioReceiveStream& operator=(const AudioReceiveStream&) = delete;
67
68 ~AudioReceiveStream() override;
69
70 // webrtc::AudioReceiveStream implementation.
71 void Reconfigure(const webrtc::AudioReceiveStream::Config& config) override;
72 void Start() override;
73 void Stop() override;
74 bool IsRunning() const override;
75
76 webrtc::AudioReceiveStream::Stats GetStats(
77 bool get_and_clear_legacy_stats) const override;
78 void SetSink(AudioSinkInterface* sink) override;
79 void SetGain(float gain) override;
80 bool SetBaseMinimumPlayoutDelayMs(int delay_ms) override;
81 int GetBaseMinimumPlayoutDelayMs() const override;
82 std::vector<webrtc::RtpSource> GetSources() const override;
83
84 // AudioMixer::Source
85 AudioFrameInfo GetAudioFrameWithInfo(int sample_rate_hz,
86 AudioFrame* audio_frame) override;
87 int Ssrc() const override;
88 int PreferredSampleRate() const override;
89
90 // Syncable
91 uint32_t id() const override;
92 absl::optional<Syncable::Info> GetInfo() const override;
93 bool GetPlayoutRtpTimestamp(uint32_t* rtp_timestamp,
94 int64_t* time_ms) const override;
95 void SetEstimatedPlayoutNtpTimestampMs(int64_t ntp_timestamp_ms,
96 int64_t time_ms) override;
97 bool SetMinimumPlayoutDelay(int delay_ms) override;
98
99 void AssociateSendStream(AudioSendStream* send_stream);
100 void DeliverRtcp(const uint8_t* packet, size_t length);
101 const webrtc::AudioReceiveStream::Config& config() const;
102 const AudioSendStream* GetAssociatedSendStreamForTesting() const;
103
104 private:
105 static void ConfigureStream(AudioReceiveStream* stream,
106 const Config& new_config,
107 bool first_time);
108
109 AudioState* audio_state() const;
110
111 SequenceChecker worker_thread_checker_;
112 webrtc::AudioReceiveStream::Config config_;
113 rtc::scoped_refptr<webrtc::AudioState> audio_state_;
114 SourceTracker source_tracker_;
115 const std::unique_ptr<voe::ChannelReceiveInterface> channel_receive_;
116 AudioSendStream* associated_send_stream_ = nullptr;
117
118 bool playing_ RTC_GUARDED_BY(worker_thread_checker_) = false;
119
120 std::unique_ptr<RtpStreamReceiverInterface> rtp_stream_receiver_;
121};
122} // namespace internal
123} // namespace webrtc
